title: One Question About A Wall Will Determine Your Personality + Kristin Did *WHAT* To A Vaping Stranger?!
description:
Kristin just wanted to have a peaceful day of shopping with her son. Instead, she ended up confronting a person who was vaping in the middle of the store. She explain what went down, but first, Cassie has a question for us. This simple question about a wall will give us some insight into our personalities.
